{"tid":28304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［警訊］港女扮處女呃男友，博加印象分仲想日後迫婚","createTime":"2016-12-08T00:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T00:56:59.000Z","uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d25e6c04f74b6dada9323f098a28a88bf6cd920","tid":28304,"uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:22:36.000Z","msg":"女友有個8婆港女FD, 我一直都討厭佢。最近聽女友講佢換左男朋友，做警察好靚仔大隻。我心想，佢又換男友？第幾個？飛左之前個文員仔？ 而且仲話為左令個男朋友覺得佢矜貴，加分，就講自己仲係處女，拍拖頭4個月唔比扑野，仲買左什麼德國制人工處血扮處女⋯ <br />\n聽講個警察扑左好似中左6合彩咁，聽晒個港女話，仲話好好珍惜佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條女廿幾歲到尾⋯ 換畫多到數唔到⋯ 去親旅行都男仔同房⋯ 唔變黑鮑就偷笑，係到扮處女⋯ 仲話過多排就迫個男仔結婚<br />\n如果你係警察，又最近扑過處女，條女又20尾⋯ 你諗你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imD8B3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FimD8B3X.jpg&h=94169bbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3c88f075acfe36b878f3e2b4f82c997757f68bf","tid":28304,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:26:41.000Z","msg":"警察...<br />\n<br />\n個結局幾好<br />\n<br />\n佢地結左婚先再拎出來恥笑"},{"pid":"d83593f5d4a939d7ecbf629819f45ef0c6187589","tid":28304,"uid":4221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38966d5857f563d2ec2b8b842586a391f3ace36d","tid":28304,"uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:41:17.000Z","msg":"其實講真話有咩所謂⋯"},{"pid":"0e59575aa2bb59944bfd9ae92a5ff35c59388747","tid":28304,"uid":9891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98d1205ee9f3fc57b3a4db05f5ffa08cadfff7d","tid":28304,"uid":18663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:56:59.000Z","msg":"所以"}]}